results.name: Smallest multiples from A129066 of primes from A171980.
comment: A129066 lists integers n such that n divides n-th Fibonacci number A000045(n) with multiples of 12 excluded, while A171980 lists possible prime divisors of elements of A129066 in the increasing order. This sequence lists smallest multiples from A129066 of primes from A171980.
results.author: _Max Alekseyev_, Jan 20 2010
